{
  "name": "Verben - Konjugation",
  "description": "Vollständige Konjugationstabelle für a-, e-, konsonantische, gemischte und i-Konjugation im Aktiv und Passiv mit ausführlichen Erklärungen",
  "content": "<div class='lf-key'><div class='lf-key-title'>Lateinische Verbkonjugation</div><div class='lf-key-body'>Die fünf Konjugationsklassen im <span class='lf-hl'>Präsensstamm</span> (Aktiv und Passiv)</div></div><h3>Was ist eine Konjugation?</h3><p>Konjugation bedeutet die <span class='lf-hl'>Beugung von Verben</span>. Im Lateinischen gibt es <strong>fünf verschiedene Konjugationsklassen</strong>, die sich durch ihren Stamm und ihre Endungen unterscheiden. Jedes Verb gehört zu einer dieser Klassen.</p><div class='lf-box lf-info'>💡 Die Endungen sind <span style='color: #ef4444; font-weight: bold;'>rot</span> markiert, Füllbuchstaben (Bindebuchstaben) <span style='color: #3b82f6; font-weight: bold;'>blau</span></div><h3>Die fünf Konjugationsklassen</h3><dl class='lf-def'><dt>a-Konjugation</dt><dd>Erkennungszeichen: Infinitiv endet auf <strong>-āre</strong> (langes ā). Beispiel: <em>amāre</em> (lieben)</dd><dt>e-Konjugation</dt><dd>Erkennungszeichen: Infinitiv endet auf <strong>-ēre</strong> (langes ē). Beispiel: <em>monēre</em> (mahnen, ermahnen)</dd><dt>konsonantische Konjugation</dt><dd>Erkennungszeichen: Infinitiv endet auf <strong>-ere</strong> (kurzes e). Beispiel: <em>regere</em> (leiten, herrschen)</dd><dt>gemischte Konjugation</dt><dd>Erkennungszeichen: Infinitiv endet auf <strong>-ere</strong> (kurzes e), aber Formen ähneln der i-Konjugation. Beispiel: <em>capere</em> (nehmen, fangen)</dd><dt>i-Konjugation</dt><dd>Erkennungszeichen: Infinitiv endet auf <strong>-īre</strong> (langes ī). Beispiel: <em>audīre</em> (hören)</dd></dl><div class='lf-box lf-tip'>✅ <strong>Merkhilfe:</strong> Die Konjugationsklasse erkennst du am <span class='lf-hl'>Infinitiv</span>! Schau dir die Endung vor dem -re an.</div><h3>Wichtige Begriffe</h3><div class='lf-two-col'><div><strong>Aktiv vs. Passiv</strong><p><em>Aktiv:</em> Das Subjekt handelt (ich liebe)<br><em>Passiv:</em> Das Subjekt wird behandelt (ich werde geliebt)</p></div><div><strong>Indikativ vs. Konjunktiv</strong><p><em>Indikativ:</em> Wirklichkeit (er liebt)<br><em>Konjunktiv:</em> Möglichkeit, Wunsch (er möge lieben)</p></div></div><h3>Stamm + Endung</h3><p>Jede Verbform besteht aus drei Teilen:</p><ol class='lf-steps'><li><strong>Verbstamm</strong> - bleibt gleich (z.B. <em>ama-</em>)</li><li><strong>Füllbuchstabe</strong> (<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>blau</span>) - verbindet Stamm und Endung</li><li><strong>Personalendung</strong> (<span style='color: #ef4444;'>rot</span>) - zeigt Person und Numerus</li></ol><div class='lf-box lf-formula'>Verbform = Stamm + Füllbuchstabe + Endung</div><h3>Personalendungen merken</h3><table class='lf-table' style='width: auto; margin: 1rem 0;'><thead><tr><th>Person</th><th>Aktiv</th><th>Passiv</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>1. Sg.</td><td>-<strong>ō</strong> / -<strong>m</strong></td><td>-<strong>or</strong> / -<strong>r</strong></td></tr><tr><td>2. Sg.</td><td>-<strong>s</strong></td><td>-<strong>ris</strong></td></tr><tr><td>3. Sg.</td><td>-<strong>t</strong></td><td>-<strong>tur</strong></td></tr><tr><td>1. Pl.</td><td>-<strong>mus</strong></td><td>-<strong>mur</strong></td></tr><tr><td>2. Pl.</td><td>-<strong>tis</strong></td><td>-<strong>mini</strong></td></tr><tr><td>3. Pl.</td><td>-<strong>nt</strong></td><td>-<strong>ntur</strong></td></tr></tbody></table><div class='lf-box lf-tip'>✅ <strong>Eselsbrücke Aktiv:</strong> <em>\"O, s, t, mus, tis, nt\"</em> - Sprich: \"O Musst ist!\"</div><h3>Präsensstamm Aktiv</h3><table class='lf-table' style='font-size: 0.9em;'><thead><tr><th style='min-width: 140px;'>Form</th><th>a-Konj.<br><small>(amāre)</small></th><th>e-Konj.<br><small>(monēre)</small></th><th>kons. Konj.<br><small>(regere)</small></th><th>gem. Konj.<br><small>(capere)</small></th><th>i-Konj.<br><small>(audīre)</small></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr style='background: rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.05);'><td colspan='6' style='font-weight: bold; text-align: center;'>Indikativ Präsens</td></tr><tr><td>1. Sg.</td><td>am<span style='color: #ef4444;'>-ō</span></td><td>mone<span style='color: #ef4444;'>-ō</span></td><td>reg<span style='color: #ef4444;'>-ō</span></td><td>capi<span style='color: #ef4444;'>-ō</span></td><td>audi<span style='color: #ef4444;'>-ō</span></td></tr><tr><td>2. Sg.</td><td>am<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>ā</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-s</span></td><td>mon<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>ē</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-s</span></td><td>reg<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>-i</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-s</span></td><td>cap<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>i</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-s</span></td><td>aud<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>ī</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-s</span></td></tr><tr><td>3. Sg.</td><td>ama<span style='color: #ef4444;'>-t</span></td><td>mone<span style='color: #ef4444;'>-t</span></td><td>reg<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>-i</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-t</span></td><td>capi<span style='color: #ef4444;'>-t</span></td><td>audi<span style='color: #ef4444;'>-t</span></td></tr><tr><td>1. Pl.</td><td>am<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>ā</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-mus</span></td><td>mon<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>ē</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-mus</span></td><td>reg<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>-i</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-mus</span></td><td>cap<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>i</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-mus</span></td><td>aud<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>ī</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-mus</span></td></tr><tr><td>2. Pl.</td><td>am<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>ā</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-tis</span></td><td>mon<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>ē</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-tis</span></td><td>reg<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>-i</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-tis</span></td><td>cap<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>i</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-tis</span></td><td>aud<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>ī</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-tis</span></td></tr><tr><td>3. Pl.</td><td>ama<span style='color: #ef4444;'>-nt</span></td><td>mone<span style='color: #ef4444;'>-nt</span></td><td>reg<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>-u</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-nt</span></td><td>cap<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>i-u</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-nt</span></td><td>aud<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>i-u</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-nt</span></td></tr><tr style='background: rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.05);'><td colspan='6' style='font-weight: bold; text-align: center;'>Konjunktiv Präsens</td></tr><tr><td>1. Sg.</td><td>am<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>e</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-m</span></td><td>mone<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>-a</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-m</span></td><td>reg<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>-a</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-m</span></td><td>cap<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>i-a</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-m</span></td><td>aud<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>i-a</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-m</span></td></tr><tr><td>2. Sg.</td><td>am<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>ē</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-s</span></td><td>mone<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>-ā</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-s</span></td><td>reg<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>-ā</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-s</span></td><td>cap<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>i-ā</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-s</span></td><td>aud<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>i-ā</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-s</span></td></tr><tr><td>3. Sg.</td><td>am<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>e</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-t</span></td><td>mone<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>-a</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-t</span></td><td>reg<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>-a</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-t</span></td><td>cap<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>i-a</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-t</span></td><td>aud<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>i-a</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-t</span></td></tr><tr><td>1. Pl.</td><td>am<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>ē</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-mus</span></td><td>mone<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>-ā</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-mus</span></td><td>reg<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>-ā</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-mus</span></td><td>cap<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>i-ā</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-mus</span></td><td>aud<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>i-ā</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-mus</span></td></tr><tr><td>2. Pl.</td><td>am<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>ē</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-tis</span></td><td>mone<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>-ā</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-tis</span></td><td>reg<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>-ā</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-tis</span></td><td>cap<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>i-ā</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-tis</span></td><td>aud<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>i-ā</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-tis</span></td></tr><tr><td>3. Pl.</td><td>am<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>e</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-nt</span></td><td>mone<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>-a</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-nt</span></td><td>reg<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>-a</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-nt</span></td><td>cap<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>i-a</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-nt</span></td><td>aud<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>i-a</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-nt</span></td></tr><tr style='background: rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.05);'><td colspan='6' style='font-weight: bold; text-align: center;'>Konjunktiv Imperfekt</td></tr><tr><td>1. Sg.</td><td>am<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>ā-re</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-m</span></td><td>mon<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>ē-re</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-m</span></td><td>reg<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>-e-re</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-m</span></td><td>cap<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>-e-re</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-m</span></td><td>aud<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>ī-re</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-m</span></td></tr><tr><td>2. Sg.</td><td>am<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>ā-rē</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-s</span></td><td>mon<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>ē-rē</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-s</span></td><td>reg<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>-e-rē</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-s</span></td><td>cap<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>-e-rē</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-s</span></td><td>aud<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>ī-rē</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-s</span></td></tr><tr><td>3. Sg.</td><td>am<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>ā-re</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-t</span></td><td>mon<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>ē-re</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-t</span></td><td>reg<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>-e-re</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-t</span></td><td>cap<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>-e-re</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-t</span></td><td>aud<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>ī-re</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-t</span></td></tr><tr><td>1. Pl.</td><td>am<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>ā-rē</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-mus</span></td><td>mon<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>ē-rē</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-mus</span></td><td>reg<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>-e-rē</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-mus</span></td><td>cap<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>-e-rē</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-mus</span></td><td>aud<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>ī-rē</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-mus</span></td></tr><tr><td>2. Pl.</td><td>am<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>ā-rē</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-tis</span></td><td>mon<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>ē-rē</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-tis</span></td><td>reg<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>-e-rē</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-tis</span></td><td>cap<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>-e-rē</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-tis</span></td><td>aud<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>ī-rē</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-tis</span></td></tr><tr><td>3. Pl.</td><td>am<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>ā-re</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-nt</span></td><td>mon<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>ē-re</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-nt</span></td><td>reg<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>-e-re</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-nt</span></td><td>cap<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>-e-re</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-nt</span></td><td>aud<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>ī-re</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-nt</span></td></tr><tr style='background: rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.05);'><td colspan='6' style='font-weight: bold; text-align: center;'>Imperativ</td></tr><tr><td>2. Sg.</td><td>ama</td><td>mone</td><td>rege</td><td>cape</td><td>audi</td></tr><tr><td>2. Pl.</td><td>am<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>ā</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-te</span></td><td>mon<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>ē</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-te</span></td><td>reg<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>-i</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-te</span></td><td>cap<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>-i</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-te</span></td><td>aud<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>ī</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-te</span></td></tr><tr style='background: rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.05);'><td colspan='6' style='font-weight: bold; text-align: center;'>Infinitiv Präsens</td></tr><tr><td></td><td>am<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>ā</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-re</span></td><td>mon<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>ē</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-re</span></td><td>reg<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>-e</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-re</span></td><td>cap<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>-e</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-re</span></td><td>aud<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>ī</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-re</span></td></tr><tr style='background: rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.05);'><td colspan='6' style='font-weight: bold; text-align: center;'>Partizip Präsens Aktiv (PPA)</td></tr><tr><td>Nom. Sg.</td><td>am<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>a</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-ns</span></td><td>mon<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>e</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-ns</span></td><td>reg<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>-e</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-ns</span></td><td>cap<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>-ie</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-ns</span></td><td>aud<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>ie</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-ns</span></td></tr><tr><td>Gen. Sg.</td><td>am<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>a</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-ntis</span></td><td>mon<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>e</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-ntis</span></td><td>reg<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>-e</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-ntis</span></td><td>cap<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>-ie</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-ntis</span></td><td>aud<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>ie</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-ntis</span></td></tr><tr style='background: rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.05);'><td colspan='6' style='font-weight: bold; text-align: center;'>Gerundivum</td></tr><tr><td></td><td>am<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>a</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-ndus</span></td><td>mon<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>e</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-ndus</span></td><td>reg<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>-e</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-ndus</span></td><td>cap<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>-ie</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-ndus</span></td><td>aud<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>ie</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-ndus</span></td></tr></tbody></table><div class='lf-box lf-tip'>✅ <strong>Konjunktiv Präsens merken:</strong> a-Konj. bekommt <span style='color: #3b82f6;'>e</span>, alle anderen bekommen <span style='color: #3b82f6;'>a</span>!</div><h3 style='margin-top: 2rem;'>Präsensstamm Passiv</h3><table class='lf-table' style='font-size: 0.9em;'><thead><tr><th style='min-width: 140px;'>Form</th><th>a-Konj.<br><small>(amāre)</small></th><th>e-Konj.<br><small>(monēre)</small></th><th>kons. Konj.<br><small>(regere)</small></th><th>gem. Konj.<br><small>(capere)</small></th><th>i-Konj.<br><small>(audīre)</small></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr style='background: rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.05);'><td colspan='6' style='font-weight: bold; text-align: center;'>Indikativ Präsens</td></tr><tr><td>1. Sg.</td><td>am<span style='color: #ef4444;'>-or</span></td><td>mone<span style='color: #ef4444;'>-or</span></td><td>reg<span style='color: #ef4444;'>-or</span></td><td>capi<span style='color: #ef4444;'>-or</span></td><td>audi<span style='color: #ef4444;'>-or</span></td></tr><tr><td>2. Sg.</td><td>am<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>ā</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-ris</span></td><td>mon<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>ē</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-ris</span></td><td>reg<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>-e</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-ris</span></td><td>cap<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>-e</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-ris</span></td><td>aud<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>ī</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-ris</span></td></tr><tr><td>3. Sg.</td><td>am<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>ā</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-tur</span></td><td>mon<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>ē</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-tur</span></td><td>reg<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>-i</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-tur</span></td><td>cap<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>-i</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-tur</span></td><td>aud<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>ī</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-tur</span></td></tr><tr><td>1. Pl.</td><td>am<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>ā</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-mur</span></td><td>mon<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>ē</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-mur</span></td><td>reg<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>-i</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-mur</span></td><td>cap<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>-i</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-mur</span></td><td>aud<span style='color: #3b82f6;'>ī</span><span style='color: #ef4444;'>-mur</span></td></tr><tr